@startuml
title Chapter 2 - Repo Architecture (Component View)

package "ch2_coords" {
  [example_coordinate_transforms.py] as ex
  [README.md] as readme
}

package "core/coords" {
  [__init__.py] as cinit
  [transforms.py] as ctrans
  [rotations.py] as crot
  [frames.py] as cframes
}

folder "data/sim/ch2_coords_san_francisco" as ds

readme ..> ex : run commands
ex --> cinit : imports
cinit --> ctrans : re-export
cinit --> crot : re-export
cinit --> cframes : re-export

ex ..> ds : optional --data
(load_dataset)

note right of ctrans
LLH/ECEF/ENU transforms
(Eq. 2.9, 2.10 + iterative inverse)
end note

note right of crot
Euler / Rotation matrix / Quaternion
(Eq. 2.17, 2.21-2.23)
end note

@enduml